KAME instllation

KAME needs following libraries;
kdelibs and others which depend on kdelibs
ruby
gsl
fftw
xerces-c++
linux-gpib (if you need GPIB)
gc (with --enable-cplusplus)
FTGL (included in source tree)

To build FTGL
in directory FTGL/unix
./configure --enable-static --disable-shared
make

To build KAME
if you use MacOS X (Tiger)
in directory macosx
./myconfigure
make

and install
make install